'''Anẓid n Tmazɣa''' d yiwen gar [[talmest|telmest]] n [[tawsit|tewsit]] n [[anẓid|inẓiden]], Yettidir di [[tmura n Tmazɣa]] id yezgan di [[Tafriqt ugafa]] 


== Assaɣen-is (ismawen-is) ==
* Assaɣ [[Taserɣint|aserɣin]]: (''السنجاب البربري'')

* Ɣer imaziɣen n Umeṛṛuk: (''Anziḍ''), (''Agbur''), (''Abgur'')

* Di tama n [[Taza]]: (''Cefcen شفشن'')

== Tiddi d wazuk ==
[[Tiddi]]-ynes ad tili gar n 20 ar 25 cm war [[asallaf]]-is Yettwassen ar 15 cm, ma d [[azuk]]-is yettili gar 200 alamma d 300g neɣ ugar

== Učči ==
Anẓid n Tmazɣa d aɣersiw [[timestuga|amestugan]] imi ytečč [[ifes|ifsan]] d kra n [[igumma]] yettaf deg tegnit am [[agusim|ugusim]], [[Adren|iderran]] akked [[isiɣid]] neɣ [[asegmar]] d [[adeffu|udeffu]], d kra n icakan neɣ [[izegza]] am [[amessa]] d [[tazant]]

== Tiɣzi n tudert ==
Mara ad yili deg [[azɣar|uzaɣar]] yettidir gar n 3 ar 5 n iseggasen, Maca mara ad yilli yettwaṭṭef ɣer [[afgan|ufgan]] yezmer ad yidir alarma d 8 n iseggasen
